        },
        {
            "title": "美國住宅建築商信心指數升幅為2024年初以來最大",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"632\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/9LWSSjmRH1X9C9Pi5yImdg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzMjtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/2328c3f9395252f908f8e848a865f577\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國住宅<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:建築商;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/建築商\">建築商</a>的信心本月升幅為2024年初以來最高，因抵押貸款利率下降，全國住房負擔能力得到改善。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國全國住宅建築商協會(NAHB)與富國銀行發布的市場狀況指數10月上升5點至37，為4月以來最高。指數低於50意味著更多建築商認為市場狀況糟糕而非良好。接受彭博調查的經濟學家預計該指數小幅上升至33。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">NAHB主席Buddy Hughes周四在一份聲明中表示：「儘管近期抵押貸款利率下降對改善負擔能力而言是一個令人鼓舞的信號，但市場仍然充滿挑戰。大多數購房者仍在觀望，等待抵押貸款利率下降。」</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-9683c2d6-e281-300b-9747-5c91e8cb45f3-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"632\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/aGjfi_lPxzBq1zLkC4A_og--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzMjtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/6e28663f4d8846cbd973d10535fa8165\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">分項數據均上漲，未來六個月銷售預期指數升至今年年初以來最高。當前銷售指標和潛在買家流量指標攀升至4月以來的最高水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">目前，建築商一直在放緩建設速度，並試圖通過降價和銷售激勵等多種方式吸引買家。根據NAHB數據，10月有38%的建築商報告降價，與最近幾個月的情況類似。更廣泛地說，65%的建築商報告採取了銷售激勵措施，這一比例與上月持平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">全國房地產經紀人協會將於10月23日發布9月二手房銷售報告。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Homebuilder Sentiment Rises By Most Since 2024 on Lower Rates</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Chris Middleton.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E5%BB%BA%E7%AF%89%E5%95%86%E4%BF%A1%E5%BF%83%E6%8C%87%E6%95%B8%E5%8D%87%E5%B9%85%E7%82%BA2024%E5%B9%B4%E5%88%9D%E4%BB%A5%E4%BE%86%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7-152719797.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-17 01:25:42",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "印度稱不知悉川普與莫迪就俄羅斯石油問題進行過交談",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 印度外交部表示，並不知悉周三美國總統唐納德·川普與總理納倫德拉·莫迪之間有過對話。此前數小時，川普曾表示他與印度領導人進行了談話，後者承諾將停止購買俄羅斯石油。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">印度外交部發言人Randhir Jaiswal周四在新德里記者會上表示，「據我們所知，我並不知悉莫迪總理與川普總統之間昨日有任何對話。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">自川普對來自這個南亞國家的商品徵收50%關稅以來，美印關係持續緊張。美國總統將此舉視為對新德里購買俄羅斯原油的懲罰。周三，川普暗示該問題或將迎來轉機。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-a3763235-5be0-3d86-ad54-723374a9f3d3-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Jaiswal在周四早些時候的聲明中雖未確認印度將滿足川普的要求，但表示新德里正致力於深化與美國的能源合作。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">莫迪政府此前曾表示，只要經濟上可行，印度將繼續購買俄羅斯石油。Jaiswal周四重申，在制定印度能源進口政策時，消費者利益仍是首要考量。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題India Says Unaware of Trump-Modi Conversation on Russian Oil (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E7%A8%B1%E4%B8%8D%E7%9F%A5%E6%82%89%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E8%88%87%E8%8E%AB%E8%BF%AA%E5%B0%B1%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E7%9F%B3%E6%B2%B9%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%E9%80%B2%E8%A1%8C%E9%81%8E%E4%BA%A4%E8%AB%87-132912754.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-16 23:45:41",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        }
